					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="640" height="457" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-53.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-53.png?w=640&amp;ssl=1 640w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-53.png?resize=204%2C146&amp;ssl=1 204w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
